# Toolbox API

This is a api create to BossaBox challenge, we can Create, List, and Delete tools.



# Group Users

## Users [/users]

### Create a new user account [POST]
You can create a new user account sending **name**, **email** and **password**.
This should return a JSON object containing user registred data in database.

+ Request (application/json)
    {  
        "name": "Kelvyn Santana",
        "email": "santanakelvyn@gmail.com",
        "password: "123456"
    }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

    {
        "name": "Kelvyn Santana",
        "email": "santanakelvyn@gmail.com",
        "createdAt": "2020-06-26T18:14:18.175Z",
        "updatedAt": "2020-06-26T18:14:18.175Z",
        "id": "5ef63afa11de980b56ce9970"
    }

# Group Authentication

## Sessions [/sessions]

### Create a new user session [POST]
To execute actions in API you need a JWT token. 
To get a JWT token you need send a JSON object with valid  **email**, and **password**, and this should return a JSON object containing **user data** and **JWT token**

+ Request (application/json)
    {
        "email": "santanakelvyn@gmail.com",
        "password: "123456
    }

+ Response 200
    {
        "user": {
            "name": "Kelvyn Santana",
            "email": "santanakelvyn@gmail.com",
            "createdAt": "2020-06-26T18:52:51.060Z",
            "updatedAt": "2020-06-26T18:52:51.060Z",
            "id": "5ef6440314881f1ac7cb543d"
        },
        "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjVlZjY0NDAzMTQ4ODFmMWFjN2NiNTQzZCIsImlhdCI6MTU5MzE5NzYwNCwiZXhwIjoxNTkzMzcwNDA0fQ.w6HLgJZSJb1ySyF3GRuQ89eK0Rzik8Qu88xxcTk_x_c"
    }

# Group Tools 

## Tools [/tools]
We have create, read, update and delete tools in application

### List [GET]
Return all tools in database.

You have added a optional query parameter `tag` to filter results by tag.



+ Response 200 (application/json)

