### Create Tool [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    
    {
        "title": "Visual Studio Code",
        "link": "https://code.visualstidio.com",
        "description": "The best and most used code editor",
        "tags": ["code", "development", "editor"]
    }

+ Response 201

    {
        "tags": [
            "code",
            "development",
            "editor"
        ],
        "title": "Visual Studio Code",
        "link": "https://code.visualstidio.com",
        "description": "The best and most used code editor",
        "createdAt": "2020-06-26T19:41:19.107Z",
        "updatedAt": "2020-06-26T19:41:19.107Z",
        "id": "5ef64f5f14881f1ac7cb543e"
    }

## Tools by Tag [/tools?tag=code]

### List by tag [GET]

+ Parameters
    + tag (string, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    {
        "tools": [
            {
            "tags": [
                "code",
                "development",
                "editor"
            ],
            "title": "Visual Studio Code",
            "link": "https://code.visualstidio.com",
            "description": "The best and most used code editor",
            "createdAt": "2020-06-26T19:41:19.107Z",
            "updatedAt": "2020-06-26T19:41:19.107Z",
            "id": "5ef64f5f14881f1ac7cb543e"
            }
        ],
        "filter": "code"
    }



